&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Create a balanced environment that encourages both iterative improvement and rigorous evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Provide clear, actionable feedback and support for engineer growth and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Help partner teams develop approaches for sharing capabilities and partnering to evolve our platform alongside the sophistication of our products and users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Drive adoption of platform capabilities and learnings to inform company-wide product strategy and planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Represent the platform perspective and roadmap in discussions with research, product, and leadership stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
