&lt;ul class=&quot;[&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-7&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Have 3+ years of engineering management experience leading high-performing teams in ambiguous, early-stage environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Excel at creating psychological safety and helping teams navigate uncertainty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Demonstrate strong interpersonal skills and ability to guide teams through rapidly evolving organization priorities while building underlying stable platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Have excellent cross-functional leadership skills to build alignment between research, engineering and product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Are skilled at facilitating decision-making rather than imposing solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Have expertise in mentoring and investing energy into team culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Have excellent communication skills to represent the importance of and need to invest in platform capabilities at the core of our products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Have a comprehensive technical understanding of modern software product development processes and technical stacks. Experience of AI/ML is a bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Care deeply about responsibly pushing the boundaries of AI capabilities in service of Anthropic&#39;s mission&lt;/li&gt;
